# Printonet Provisioning API Contract

## Endpoint

- `POST /wp-json/printonet/v1/provision-store`
- `POST /wp-json/printonet/v1/slug-availability`
- `POST /wp-json/printonet/v1/tenant/config`
- `POST /wp-json/printonet/v1/suppliers/sync`
- `POST /wp-json/printonet/v1/suppliers/validate`
- `GET /wp-json/printonet/v1/suppliers/sync-status/{job_id}`
- `POST /wp-json/printonet/v1/suppliers/webhook`

## Authentication

- Preferred signed request headers:
  - `X-Printonet-Timestamp: <unix_epoch_seconds>`
  - `X-Printonet-Signature: <hex_hmac_sha256(timestamp + "." + raw_body, PLATFORM_HMAC_SECRET)>`
- Optional legacy fallback (only if `PRINTONET_ALLOW_LEGACY_API_KEY=true`):
  - `X-Printonet-Api-Key: <PROVISIONING_API_KEY>`

Replay protection:

- A valid signature can only be used once for the same method/route/timestamp/signature tuple.
- Reuse inside the 5-minute window is rejected.

## Request body

```json
{
  "tenant_slug": "acme-print",
  "request_id": "optional-idempotency-key-123",
  "store_name": "Acme Print",
  "admin_email": "owner@acmeprint.com",
  "admin_username": "acme_owner",
  "admin_password": "optional-strong-password",
  "primary_color": "#0f172a",
  "secondary_color": "#f8fafc",
  "logo_url": "https://cdn.printonet.com/logos/acme.png",
  "currency": "USD",
  "default_country": "US:CA",
  "weight_unit": "lbs",
  "dimension_unit": "in"
}
```

Slug policy:

- lowercase letters, numbers, hyphens only
- max length: 40
- reserved slugs blocked (`www`, `admin`, `api`, `support`, `stores`, etc.)

## Slug availability request

```json
{
  "store_name": "Great Prints"
}
```

or

```json
{
  "tenant_slug": "greatprints"
}
```

## Slug availability response

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "tenant_slug": "greatprints",
  "available": false,
  "domain": "greatprints.stores.printonet.com",
  "suggestions": ["greatprints-shop", "greatprints-co"]
}
```

## Tenant config update request

Use this to push dashboard-driven config to each tenant store.

```json
{
  "status": "active",
  "branding": {
    "store_name": "Great Prints",
    "logo_url": "https://cdn.printonet.com/logos/greatprints.png",
    "primary_color": "#0f172a",
    "secondary_color": "#f8fafc",
    "font_family": "Inter, sans-serif"
  },
  "layout": {
    "hero_style": "split"
  },
  "homepage_sections": [
    { "id": "hero", "enabled": true },
    { "id": "featured_products", "enabled": true }
  ]
}
```

`status` values:

- `active`
- `suspended` (checkout/purchasing blocked)

## Success response

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "site_id": 12,
  "admin_user_id": 56,
  "store_url": "https://acme-print.stores.printonet.local"
}
```

If `request_id` is reused, endpoint returns existing tenant info with:

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "idempotent": true,
  "site_id": 12,
  "admin_user_id": 56,
  "store_url": "https://acme-print.stores.printonet.local"
}
```

## Error responses

- `401/403`: invalid API key
- `409`: tenant already exists
- `422`: missing required fields
- `500`: site creation failure

## Supplier sync request

```json
{
  "supplier": "printonet_internal",
  "credentials": {
    "base_url": "https://qumrnazgdrijdcihtkah.supabase.co/functions/v1/tenant-catalog-feed",
    "tenant_slug": "stores.printonet.com"
  }
}
```

If `supplier` is omitted, default is `printonet_internal`.

## Supplier sync response

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "queued": true,
  "job_id": 101,
  "supplier": "printonet_internal"
}
```

## Supplier validation request

```json
{
  "supplier": "printful",
  "credentials": {
    "api_key": "supplier-token"
  }
}
```

For Printify, include `shop_id`:

```json
{
  "supplier": "printify",
  "credentials": {
    "api_key": "supplier-token",
    "shop_id": "123456"
  }
}
```

For internal supplier validation:

```json
{
  "supplier": "printonet_internal",
  "credentials": {
    "base_url": "https://qumrnazgdrijdcihtkah.supabase.co/functions/v1/tenant-catalog-feed"
  }
}
```

Internal supplier call contract:

- Method: `GET {base_url}?tenant_slug={slug}&limit=200`
- Headers:
  - `X-Printonet-Timestamp: <unix_seconds>`
  - `X-Printonet-Signature: hex(HMAC-SHA256("${timestamp}.", PLATFORM_HMAC_SECRET))`

Internal supplier response schema must return:

```json
{
  "items": [
    {
      "sku": "TSHIRT-001",
      "name": "Soft Cotton Tee",
      "price": 24.99,
      "stock": 120
    }
  ]
}
```

Validation rules:

- `items` must be an array
- every item must include non-empty string `sku` and `name`
- every item must include numeric `price` and `stock`

## Supplier status response

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "job": {
    "id": 101,
    "blog_id": 12,
    "supplier": "printful",
