  }
}
```

## Supplier webhook request

Authentication header:

- `X-Printonet-Webhook-Secret: <SUPPLIER_WEBHOOK_SECRET>`

Body:

```json
{
  "event": "stock_price_update",
  "blog_id": 12,
  "items": [
    { "sku": "TSHIRT-001", "price": "24.99", "stock": 120 },
    { "sku": "TSHIRT-002", "stock": 0 }
  ]
}
```
